{"id":394127,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/05/新浪微博｜向五毛宣战/","date":"2015-05-31T20:26:13Z","modified":"2015-05-31T20:57:29Z","title":"【微博】荣剑：向五毛宣战","content":"<p><a class=\"W_texta W_fb\" title=\"荣剑2001\" href=\"http://weibo.com/u/5459181838\" target=\"_blank\">荣剑2001 </a>：【向五毛宣战】吁请国家网络主管部门，督促新浪微博公司，动员广大有正义感和良知感的网民，发动一场彻底清除网上污言秽语的清网运动。当前横行着一个庞大群体，他们来路不明，无名无姓，不讲道理，无视法律，以污言秽语为武器，以人身攻击为快事，污染网络，毒化精神空间，不彻底清除之是本国的耻辱!</p>\n<p><a class=\"W_texta W_fb\" title=\"荣剑2001\" href=\"http://weibo.com/u/5459181838\" target=\"_blank\">荣剑2001 </a>：今天发的向五毛宣战帖，真是热闹，引来了<span class=\"red\">胡锡进</span>连发两个评论，这位环球时报的总编的确不易，几乎每发一个帖子都会招来骂声，包括不忍卒读的污言秽语，我对他深表同情，尽管有时也难免有点快意。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-394128\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttew4zhj30k00zkah4.jpg\" alt=\"005XsazYjw1esnttew4zhj30k00zkah4\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttew4zhj30k00zkah4.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttew4zhj30k00zkah4-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-394129\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttfqi4oj30k00zkagq.jpg\" alt=\"005XsazYjw1esnttfqi4oj30k00zkagq\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttfqi4oj30k00zkagq.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttfqi4oj30k00zkagq-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-394130\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttg6a4jj30k00zktez.jpg\" alt=\"005XsazYjw1esnttg6a4jj30k00zktez\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005XsazYjw1esnttg6a4jj30k00zktez.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/05/005Xs